# Digital Trust Shield public repository guardrails
#
# This repository is intended to publish the product idea, architecture, demo
# flow, and setup notes. The private signing, verification, watermarking, key
# handling, and production integration code is intentionally not published.

# Secrets, private keys, Firebase credentials, and runtime configuration
.env
*.env
backend/.env
backend/secrets/
backend/secure_private_keys/
*private_key*
*.pem
*.key
*.enc
!.env.example
!backend/.env.example

# Core proprietary signing and verification engine
# These files contain the RSA signing, perceptual fingerprinting, DCT
# watermarking, PDF/video support, registry matching, and screenshot recovery
# implementation. Keep them private; describe the approach in README/docs.
app.py
generate_keys.py
secure_private_key.py
sign_poster.py
verify_poster.py
watermark_embedder.py
watermark_extractor.py
utils.py
pdf_support.py
video_support.py
__init__.py

# Full backend implementation
# Public repo documents the API architecture only. The production FastAPI
# implementation remains private to protect security-sensitive logic.
backend/app/
backend/uploads/
backend/temp_uploads/
backend/temp_outputs/

# Full frontend and Android implementation
# Public repo documents the interfaces and workflow only. The app source remains
# private so API wiring and implementation details are not exposed.
admin-portal/src/
admin-portal/node_modules/
admin-portal/dist/
admin-portal/.env
android-verifier/app/src/
android-verifier/app/build/
android-verifier/build/
android-verifier/.gradle/
android-verifier/local.properties

# Generated runtime state and audit output
official_registry.json
audit_logs/
demo_runtime/
*.log

# QA/test/generated images, PDFs, and screenshots
qa_final_check/
qa_matrix/
qa_matrix_after_patch/
qa_pdf/
qa_quality/
qa_real_images/
qa_screenshot/
qa_screenshot_registry/
qa_tune/
qa_tune_rep/

